INSERT INTO accounts (
                user_id,
                provider,
                provider_account_id,
                refresh_token,
                expires_at,
                token_type
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            RETURNING 
                id,
                user_id,
                provider,
                provider_account_id,
                refresh_token,
                expires_at as "expires_at: DateTime<Utc>",
                token_type,
                updated_at as "updated_at: DateTime<Utc>",
                created_at as "created_at: DateTime<Utc>"
